### Rules
- Deterministic tools (`# DETERMINISTIC`) must remain pure Python — no LLM calls, no network I/O
- All tool implementations must include type annotations and a one-line docstring
- Do **not** move deterministic tools into `tools=[...]` — they are called directly in `agent.py`

